{
  "3335020": {
    "name": "《Wartales》扩展包：斯凯尔玛入侵",
    "steam_appid": 3335020,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335020/extras/c90cf997035ee3872f474fe29e62628e.webp?t=1752585310\" width=614 height=62 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335020/extras/4a94fd92d3e8ccbb2e2bd052297f2a35.poster.avif?t=1752585310\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335020/extras/4a94fd92d3e8ccbb2e2bd052297f2a35.webm?t=1752585310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335020/extras/4a94fd92d3e8ccbb2e2bd052297f2a35.mp4?t=1752585310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>深入奥曼斯，这片曾经坚不可摧的土地，如今却在史上最猛烈的入侵中陷落。斯凯尔玛人首次团结在一起，由被神明选中的残酷的高贵领主斯文率领，集结了部落的力量，誓要抢夺爱多兰的财富和肥沃土地。这前所未有的部落联盟席卷了整个区域，所到之处尽是废墟和混乱。<br><br>最后要塞已失守，守军四散逃亡，你将解救被困的女伯爵，集结幸存的军队，解放每一个小领地，将斯凯尔玛大军逐出。投身这场激烈的战斗，重建奥曼斯，守护爱多兰免于灭亡。你准备好收复这片土地了吗？<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335020/extras/207a6e477991448e4e099825af53b919.webp?t=1752585310\" width=614 height=62 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335020/extras/1c658b0a7d0d0725cf9fc9a1df53d394.poster.avif?t=1752585310\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335020/extras/1c658b0a7d0d0725cf9fc9a1df53d394.webm?t=1752585310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335020/extras/1c658b0a7d0d0725cf9fc9a1df53d394.mp4?t=1752585310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>一步步收复奥曼斯的各个领地，你将面对的是满目疮痍的土地，这片土地自被斯凯尔玛人占领后，陷入混乱并被战争所摧残。斯凯尔玛人牢牢掌控每一座要塞和重要地点，而其他地方则被破坏殆尽，无法使用，除非你将侵略者逐出。<br><br>要解放每个领地，你需要集中力量击败中心要塞的敌人，让这片土地重新焕发生机。当地的盟友将从藏身处现身承认你的努力；投入资源还能重建被毁的地点，恢复其功能，为战争提供更强有力的支援。但只要要塞还在斯凯尔玛人的掌控之下，这片领地就仍处于敌军的控制中。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335020/extras/de9baf9fb3043fe64e44ce5bd05a69a8.webp?t=1752585310\" width=614 height=62 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335020/extras/4e3290bad4e9d7962c7b29440e2813ad.poster.avif?t=1752585310\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335020/extras/4e3290bad4e9d7962c7b29440e2813ad.webm?t=1752585310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335020/extras/4e3290bad4e9d7962c7b29440e2813ad.mp4?t=1752585310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在奥曼斯集结战争力量，击退斯凯尔玛入侵者。在已解放的区域中，可以召集当地势力加入战斗。每个地点都可以生产宝贵资源或提供独特支援，比如农场能增加补给，哨塔能提供军事支援。明智地选择并建立强大的抵抗网络，每解放一片区域，都能增强战斗实力，推动奥曼斯的收复之路。<br><br>你需要管理三大关键战争资源：人力，用来招募本地的精锐战士加入战斗；建材，用于重建被毁的地标和重要设施；补给，以保障部队的粮草和装备。 <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335020/extras/45a516dc0d17da75a62203d4bb8d23a6.webp?t=1752585310\" width=614 height=62 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335020/extras/942b17fad36ff490f484b44f1066231f.poster.avif?t=1752585310\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335020/extras/942b17fad36ff490f484b44f1066231f.webm?t=1752585310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335020/extras/942b17fad36ff490f484b44f1066231f.mp4?t=1752585310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>准备迎接激烈的要塞攻防战吧，每场战斗都可以分为两个紧张刺激的阶段。聚集你的部队在要塞外，与守卫城墙的敌军展开对决。你的盟友或许已经先行开战，击破大门打开缺口，让你的士兵冲入要塞。<br><br>大门被攻破后，便能深入要塞核心。在要塞内部与敌军交锋，击败其首领便能取得胜利。但要小心周围的哨塔，它们会持续射箭压制你的部队，直到你成功将其摧毁。这是夺回奥曼斯的关键时刻，从斯凯尔玛人的铁蹄中收复这片土地吧！",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 简体中文, 韩语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
